682
00:59:33,000 --> 00:59:34,365
Dia cuma pura-pura.

683
00:59:35,320 --> 00:59:36,268
Jangan ganggu dia!

684
00:59:36,293 --> 00:59:37,346
Dia masih hidup!

685
00:59:37,920 --> 00:59:39,160
<i>Saya suka dipeluk.</i>

686
00:59:43,320 --> 00:59:45,800
Saya memang berharap,
kalau dia masih hidup.

687
00:59:47,840 --> 00:59:50,310
Saya tahu, harapan seperti itu
takkan hidupkan dia semula.

688
00:59:59,000 --> 01:00:01,571
Mari sini.

